## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-104">分离式提供程序托管的应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-104">Decoupled providers are hosted by an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-105">两种方法可以由应用程序用于提供 WMI 类的实例： 发布/撤消或回调方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-105">Two methods can be used by the application to make instances of WMI classes available: publish/revoke or the callback method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-106">回调方法使用<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A>和<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-106">The callback method uses the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A> and <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-107">在发布/revoke 模型中，WMI 基础结构提供默认行为的许多必须在回调方法中自行编写的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-107">In the publish/revoke model, the WMI infrastructure provides default behavior for many of the methods you have to write yourself in the callback method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-108">其中包括枚举和绑定方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-108">These include the enumeration and bind methods.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-109">在此模型中，应用程序创建实例，并将其发布。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-109">In this model, the application creates instances and publishes them.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-110">应用程序负责确保类的键属性会遵循。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-110">The application is responsible for ensuring that the key properties of the classes are respected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-111">此外，应用程序负责正在删除实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-111">The application is also responsible for deleting instances.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-112">在回调模型中，WMI 基础结构要求应用程序可以处理枚举、 绑定和实现提供程序的功能所需的任何其他方法的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-112">In the callback model, the WMI infrastructure expects the application to have methods that handle enumeration, binding and any other methods required to implement the functionality of the provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-113">它将对此功能的应用程序，如果它不存在或未正确实现失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-113">It calls into the application for this functionality and fails if it does not exist or is not implemented properly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-114">应用程序注册其 WMI 类的类型与基础结构通过调用<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A>，并指示它不再需要通过调用公开的 WMI 类<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-114">The application registers the type of its WMI classes with the infrastructure by calling <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.RegisterType%2A> and indicates that it no longer wants the WMI classes exposed by calling <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.InstrumentationManager.UnregisterType%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-115">下面的示例演示如何使用发布/revoke 模型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-115">The following example demonstrates how to use the publish/revoke model.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-116">路由器类的两个实例创建和发布。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-116">Two instances of the router class are created and published.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-117">更高版本被吊销。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-117">They are later revoked.</span></span>  
  
```  
public class Sample_InstanceProvider  
{  
public int Main (string[] args)   
{  
Router r_one = new Router ();  
r_one.Name = "one";  
InstrumentationManager.Publish(r_one);  
Router r_two = new Router ();  
r_two.Name = "two";  
InstrumentationManager.Publish(r_two);  
// ....  
InstrumentationManager.Revoke(r_one);  
InstrumentationManager.Revoke(r_two);  
return 0;  
}  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="b2c15-118">在下一步的示例中，注册的回调方法用于将 RouterNew 类公开。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2c15-118">In the next example, the callback method of registration is used to expose the RouterNew class.</span></span>  
  
```  
public int MainNew(string[] args)   
{  
    InstrumentationManager.RegisterType(typeof(RouterNew));  
    // ....  
    InstrumentationManager.UnRegisterType(typeof(RouterNew));  
    return 0;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
  
```  
static int Main(string[] args)  
{  
   InstrumentationManager.RegisterType(typeof(MySampleProvider));  
   return 0;  
}  
```
